description: DEMOLITION OF EXISTING BUILDINGS AND REDEVELOPMENT OF SITE TO PROVIDE OFFICES (1201 SQ.M - CLASS B1) AND RESIDENTIAL (99 UNITS - CLASS C3) ACCOMDATION IN BUILDINGS OF TWO - SIX STOREYS, PROVISION OF CAR PARKING (24 CARS, 12 DISABLED SPACES), CYCLE PARKING (224 SPACES), VEHICLE ACCESS, LANDSCAPING, PLANT AND ASSOCIATED WORKS.
